Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:16.87,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}現在的你 全力支持著我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.87,0:00:20.62,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而現在的我 也有了支持你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.62,0:00:26.63,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使彷徨無助 我們也要結伴前行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:28.75,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}奔向未來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:38.76,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然與朋友們嬉戲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:40.52,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,250)}這樣一路走來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:44.52,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻依然感到內心的空虛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:46.69,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受盡冷漠的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.69,0:00:51.86,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}寄身於時代的狂風中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:01:00.49,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}勇氣與不安 如影相隨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:08.38,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}因此 現在就要用我的雙手創造未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:14.55,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}那些讓我們受傷感到絕望的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:18.89,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些令我們哭泣感到難過的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:20.85,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然縈繞於心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:24.85,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們終將跨過重重障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.85,0:01:29.11,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,600)}以超越所有人為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:16.87,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}君が今僕を支えて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.87,0:00:20.62,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕が今君を支える
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.62,0:00:26.63,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だから迷いながらも共に生きていこうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:28.75,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}未来へと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:38.76,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲間と戯れ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:40.52,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,250)}それなりで居ても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:44.52,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もの足りなさを感じてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:46.69,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷めた目で見られて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.69,0:00:51.86,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}乾いた時代の風に吹かれている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:01:00.49,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}不安な心と勇気が背中合わせになっている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:08.38,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}だけど今なら夢をこの手で叶えてみせるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:14.55,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}傷ついて壊れそうな日も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:18.89,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙して困らせる日も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:20.85,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あるけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:24.85,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕達はそれを越えていくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.85,0:01:29.11,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,600)}誰より上を目指して
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:46.35,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟在哪裏呢？{\fad(300,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:50.18,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於我的寶藏{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:56.23,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在即將展開大冒險{\fad(100,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:59.86,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柔和的陽光{\fad(300,300)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:01.90,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶給我啟程的預感{\fad(100,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:06.16,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 天空和花朵都在向我微笑{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:10.87,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在前方等待我的將是什麼呢？{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:13.00,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深呼吸{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:18.79,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕輕開啟夢想之門…{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:21.17,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「  走吧！」{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:23.51,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使狂風吹襲{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:25.18,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使內心動搖{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:29.89,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使手中握著的是空白的地圖{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:31.68,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使狂風吹襲{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:33.56,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要描繪美好的明天{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.56,0:21:38.19,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著遠方  去往何方？ 直到那最終的彼方{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:40.15,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決不言敗{\fad(500,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.15,0:21:41.94,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決不哭泣{\fad(500,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.94,0:21:46.70,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到夢想成真的那一天{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:48.78,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空在微笑{\fad(300,300)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.78,0:21:50.45,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花兒也在微笑{\fad(100,300)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.45,0:21:54.33,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天我也一定會開懷大笑{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.50,0:21:58.84,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何艱難險阻都能跨越{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.84,0:22:04.13,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也 再也…不會害怕了{\fad(200,700)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:46.35,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どこにあるのかな{\fad(300,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:50.18,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ボクだけの宝物{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:56.23,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今 大きな冒険へ{\fad(100,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:59.86,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,やわらかな日差し{\fad(300,300)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:01.90,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅立ちの予感{\fad(100,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:06.16,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空も花も ホラ 笑っている{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:10.87,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この先には何が待つのだろう？{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:13.00,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深呼吸{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:18.79,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢の扉にそっと手をかけて…{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:21.17,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「  行こう！」{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:23.51,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風に吹かれながら{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:25.18,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心揺らしながら{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:29.89,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真っ白な地図を片手に持ちながら{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:31.68,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風に吹かれながら{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:33.56,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日を描きながら{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.56,0:21:38.19,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠くまで 何処まで？ たどり着けるまで{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:40.15,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絶対負けないよ{\fad(500,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.15,0:21:41.94,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絶対泣かないよ{\fad(500,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.94,0:21:46.70,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この夢を叶えるその日までは{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:48.78,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あの空は笑っていた{\fad(300,300)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.78,0:21:50.45,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あの花は笑っていた{\fad(100,300)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.45,0:21:54.33,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ボクもいつか笑うから{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.50,0:21:58.84,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どんな壁も越えるから{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.84,0:22:04.13,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう 何も 何も…コワクナイ{\fad(200,700)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【註釋】
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.48,0:09:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏的斷點過多 就很難保持棋型完整
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.48,0:09:47.90,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「斷點」：在己方可以連子的地方被對手下子切斷了聯繫的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四屆北部地區中學夏季圍棋大賽參賽申請書
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大賽委員長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本中學申請參加第四屆北部地區中學圍棋大賽團體賽 我們將遵守大賽制定的規則 不會出現舞弊等行為
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如有違反 我們甘願接受取消參賽資格\n停止比賽的等處罰 不會有任何異議
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參賽中學 葉瀨區立中學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附：參賽選手如下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選手姓名   年級
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【對白】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.13,0:00:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安時代的棋師 藤原佐為
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.43,0:00:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿越了遙遠的時空 在進藤光的心中復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.27,0:00:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了領悟「神之一手」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.10,0:01:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算上貼目 相差12目半
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.37,0:01:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.75,0:01:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥 給錢吧 一萬日元
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.10,0:01:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45}{\fnsimhei}{\bord2}{\i1}{\3c&H000000&}{\pos(420,381)}你是三將
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.57,0:02:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所願 我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.94,0:02:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把那一萬日元給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.62,0:02:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是不加入圍棋社我就不給你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.59,0:02:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會加入吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.92,0:02:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是加入的話沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.51,0:02:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我再也不能去那個圍棋會場了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.43,0:02:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得還我20日元哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.68,0:02:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.24,0:02:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來下棋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.35,0:02:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一局一千日元
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.50,0:02:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不要賭錢了 畢竟這裏是圍棋社嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.34,0:02:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我執白可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.51,0:02:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以 隨便你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.63,0:02:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三谷 你可不要作弊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三谷!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筒井學長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:03:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三谷說他要加入圍棋社
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說以後不會作弊了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在因為上次我騙你連下了兩手鬧彆扭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為你笨才會上當
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽進藤說了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在整地的時候作弊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不止那樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還偷偷移動棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.82,0:03:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是把棋子藏在口袋裏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整地的時候拿出來用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.80,0:03:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就是戰無不勝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.38,0:03:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只是說說罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.54,0:03:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙的性子有點彆扭 故意這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.21,0:03:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.33,0:03:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 三谷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.71,0:03:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.51,0:03:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天上家政課的時候做了一些餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要嘗嘗看嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你 筒井學長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.59,0:03:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以吃嗎? 肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以是可以啦 不過你不會再作弊了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是一個大嘴巴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.61,0:04:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我也沒說錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只跟筒井學長和小明說過而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會作弊了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會不會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光也來點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.06,0:04:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 這樣我們就能參加大賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大賽?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不參加那玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!? 你說什麼呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是為了參加大賽才把你拉來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰管你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是參賽選手 已經決定了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不幹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准說不干啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筒井學長 你快勸勸他啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他既然不肯 我們也不必勉強他參賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.82,0:04:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能這樣呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.63,0:04:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在再去找人已經來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.75,0:04:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大賽馬上就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:04:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒海王的目標要怎麼實現啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算他去參賽我們也不可能贏海王的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海王的實力真的很強
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.01,0:05:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是個中學生的社團嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本想像不到海王有多強大!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.45,0:05:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是上次大賽筒井學長不是贏了海王嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…因為…對方的失誤…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.64,0:05:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那種程度你竟然還說我想像不到?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.82,0:05:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我贏給你們看看?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三谷…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說你願意參加大賽了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.47,0:05:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會當著你的面打敗海王的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.99,0:05:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不清楚海王的實力 真可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說過了嗎? 我可是戰無不勝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.23,0:05:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…他想在跟海王的比賽中作弊嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海王的人一定會發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.96,0:06:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉瀨中學的圍棋社會變成什麼樣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真是輸慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝承讓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次不討論棋局可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我也應該作個了斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過幾天就是大賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.02,0:06:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尹老師可能很快就要宣佈參賽選手的名單了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了避免到時候因為主將的人選惹人非議
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.37,0:07:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該讓大家都看清楚我和塔矢的差距比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔矢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.27,0:07:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我下一局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是初次對局 分先下可以吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.62,0:07:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長 大賽的主將、副將和三將
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.65,0:07:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是按照棋力決定的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也有例外的組隊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.25,0:07:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一般都是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們專心下自己的棋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進藤 快了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.04,0:08:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很快就能…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.93,0:08:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你對局了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.12,0:08:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔矢 葉瀨中學的參賽申請表送來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進藤是三將!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.34,0:08:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出於戰術上的考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.79,0:08:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的組隊不會按照棋力高低來安排
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕這個叫三谷的孩子是實力最差的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們可能打算放棄主將戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.54,0:08:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保留實力對戰餘下的兩局
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以由三年級的部長筒井擔任副將
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而進藤則是三將
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.60,0:08:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 請讓我擔任三將
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.38,0:08:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:08:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我考慮考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可否認
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.64,0:09:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也認為只有你才能跟進藤一較高下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝承讓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實力的差距很明顯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過獎了 學長的實力遠在我想像之上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.12,0:09:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是技不如人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的棋步比我考慮得遠得多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.57,0:09:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對於中央部分過於執著了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易連上這邊的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是以後就一直疲於防守
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.53,0:09:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無還手之力了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我放棄做職業棋手果然是明智的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.21,0:10:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 先暫停一下對局聽我說兩句話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於這次的大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他學校的參賽申請表都送到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然晚了一點 現在就宣佈我校的參賽隊員
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是男子組
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.67,0:10:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主將
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.34,0:10:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年級 塔矢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副將
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年級 岸本
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.25,0:10:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三將
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年級 久野
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}是塔矢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}他是大將啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}他在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是女子組…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.07,0:10:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不是答應讓我擔任三將的嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.60,0:10:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桑原老師 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒見到你露面了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.38,0:11:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好 事先打個招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下個月的棋聖戰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經決定由我來挑戰你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請多多關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.19,0:11:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經獲悉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.79,0:11:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您讓緒方輸得心服口服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像您這把年紀 還真是難得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真佩服您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你也不年輕了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不是頂著4、5個頭銜…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第5個頭銜我還打算從老師您那裏拿到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:12:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那些年輕人真是不中用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.50,0:12:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使拿到頭銜也馬上就會被別人奪走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幾年新上來的也很少有讓人眼前一亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.77,0:12:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,院生的水平變差了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的兒子現在怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.58,0:12:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說他不是院生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.35,0:12:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他經常跟我對局
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.39,0:12:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也常和來訪的棋士對局
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在圍棋的學習上並沒有怠慢過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.77,0:12:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還不參加職業考試嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.15,0:12:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在加入了中學的圍棋社
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你加入海王圍棋社的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.60,0:12:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並沒有說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然校長說你的加入能夠激勵社員
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.48,0:13:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也就不再干涉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 參加大賽又是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.26,0:13:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以你的實力去參加中學社團的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說也太輕率了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.75,0:13:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於現在的我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.51,0:13:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有心思去顧及別人的看法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.03,0:13:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要進藤光參加社團的圍棋大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就也一定要參加
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 我這麼說也許太自以為是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.98,0:13:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我的目標是父親您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.77,0:13:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的自信與自負
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是依靠自己的努力積累起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.72,0:13:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經以為只要不斷前進就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.11,0:14:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不斷前進
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能接近「神之一手」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本毫無還手之力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.15,0:14:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在進藤光面前…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.59,0:14:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他跟父親您不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟緒方先生也不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的出現給我帶來了巨大的壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在腦中只是想著怎樣才能超越他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.55,0:14:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使心中充滿畏懼也會勇於面對…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.84,0:14:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這樣才能使人成長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.12,0:14:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是以前的你無法做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在戰慄中追趕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在畏懼中挑戰 只有這樣的你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:15:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能真正地逐漸接近「神之一手」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師! 您不是答應讓我擔任三將的嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.89,0:15:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師不也說過\n能夠與進藤一較高下的人只有我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我就是為了跟他對戰才…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.63,0:15:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔矢!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是中學的社團活動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我始終堅持認為應該由實力最強的人擔任主將
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅如此!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.03,0:15:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且海王中學圍棋社還是其他學校的典範
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.69,0:15:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的確說過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.87,0:15:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠與葉瀨中學的進藤一較高下的人只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.73,0:15:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.54,0:15:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是教育的學府
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作為教師 無法違背自己的原則
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主將就是你!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次就好…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這次大賽…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要這一次就好…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次大賽結束後 我會退出圍棋社!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.90,0:16:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師! 我…!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.38,0:16:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.43,0:16:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔矢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.61,0:17:06.57,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&H5&}{\c&H372D28&\an8\move(390,55,390,-389)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\fs45\bord0}第\n四\n屆\n北\n部\n地\n區
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.61,0:17:06.57,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&H5&}{\c&H372D28&\an8\move(220,55,220,-389)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\fs50\bord0}中\n學\n夏\n季\n圍\n棋\n大\n賽\n會\n場
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.93,0:17:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}怎麼辦啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}好激動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.83,0:17:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}下得不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.73,0:17:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}好緊張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.96,0:17:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}好可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.33,0:17:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}會變成什麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}嘿嘿 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  三谷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 還以為你不會來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為你怕了海王不敢來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼傻話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個黑子 逃掉了也沒什麼好下場哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果逃走的話 另一片黑子就會被吃掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…吵死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.59,0:17:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筒井學長…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.31,0:17:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三谷 為什麼你這麼強還要作弊啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 找到了 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.05,0:18:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小明?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不用來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你看也看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.82,0:18:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近筒井學長教了我一些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提子或是數目什麼的我都懂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 難得人家做了便當送過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小明好偉大!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.07,0:18:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三谷也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.49,0:18:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤崎 我帶你去物品存放處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.16,0:18:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三谷 我們來下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去真的沒問題嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是葉瀨中學的進藤嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.43,0:18:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進藤?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉瀨的?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.14,0:18:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他上次大賽贏了海王哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:18:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他那時才小學六年級
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.84,0:19:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扮成中學生來參加比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.46,0:19:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是當時他精湛的棋藝讓周圍的人驚嘆不已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.37,0:19:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼好苦惱的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要盡全力就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.21,0:19:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全力全力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要打敗第一回合的三將…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的覺得這麼簡單嗎? 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.88,0:19:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方也會全力以赴的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.44,0:19:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真囉嗦 我的目標可是海王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以在第一回合就輸掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.43,0:19:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再全力把第二回合的海王擊敗的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.98,0:19:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定就能…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.44,0:19:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海王的三將也會盡全力的 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待跟海王的比賽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.07,0:19:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海王的三將會是什麼樣的人呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.66,0:19:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.06,0:20:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海王的三將是我 進藤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.42,0:20:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔矢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…你會…?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.05,0:20:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記不記得你說過不會再跟我下棋了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.74,0:20:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你還說要參加圍棋大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.10,0:20:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於讓我等到今天了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.63,0:20:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔矢…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了追趕佐為…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【GoGo】
