Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.55,0:22:28.31,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就走這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.10,0:22:32.66,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再下這裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.71,0:22:34.46,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再想一想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.63,0:22:37.31,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但答案的確是這三個地方的其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:42.37,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:44.88,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H000000&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\bord2}{\pos(330,383)}{\fs25}{\fad(484,300)}雖然被提掉一子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.33,0:22:46.25,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.25,0:22:48.49,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.49,0:22:49.70,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把白子提走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.43,0:22:52.53,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優希很厲害嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.39,0:22:52.39,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord3\pos(306,359)}{\1c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&HFF0000&}{\fad(0,434)}幹得好                       優希!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.36,0:22:56.05,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來年也請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.13,0:22:57.27,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\pos(329,351)}{\1c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&HFF0000&}2002年也請多多關照!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【下回預告】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯… 你們就是海王嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.36,0:23:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你們很強
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.15,0:23:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但上次還是輸給葉瀨中學吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.93,0:23:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三谷他可是我們名副其實的主將!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.88,0:23:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟他下就知道了!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.98,0:23:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不會讓你笑到最後的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.08,0:23:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是決勝負

